name: Zone 2 Endurance 40min
description:
Zone 2 training is one of the most important aspects of any training plan. We don't always get faster by training faster. In Zone 2 training, we stimulate your type 1 muscle fibres (slow-twitch). 



Spending time in Zone 2 is essential to improving performance.
